      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="rss-info">
      <h3>Subscribe to Our RSS Feed</h3>
      <p>Get every update delivered to your favourite feed reader. Never miss a story, event, or community moment.</p>
    </div>
    <a href="/feed.xml" class="btn btn-cta" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      Subscribe via RSS →
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

